Question: Do the jacket and the bat have the same color?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the jacket and the bat are black.

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='jacket')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='bat')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the jacket?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the bat?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
